      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks, that's a good start. Could you make it sound a bit more personal though? Maybe add a sentence or two that acknowledges how difficult the decision was for the hiring team specifically, since he was such a strong contender. Just something that feels a bit more 'human' so it doesn't feel like a template.",
